              "label": "Message",
              "value": "Aah gotcha! \u00f0\u009f\u0098\u0084\n\nTo check **your friends\u00e2\u0080\u0099 birthdays today** on Facebook:\n\n1. **Web (PC)**\n   - Left sidebar \u00e2\u0086\u0092 **Events**\n   - Click **Birthdays**\n\n2. **Mobile App**\n   - Tap the **\u00e2\u0080\u009cSee All\u00e2\u0080\u009d** under **Birthdays** on the Home screen, or\n   - Search **\u00e2\u0080\u009cBirthdays\u00e2\u0080\u009d** in the Facebook search bar.\n\nYou\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll see a list of friends with birthdays **today, upcoming, and recent**.\n\nIf you want an **automated reminder** (so you never miss a wish), I can guide you on setting up **Facebook birthday notifications** or using tools like **IFTTT** to send auto-messages.\n\nWii na? Want me to walk you through setting up reminders or check another date?"
