              "label": "Message",
              "value": "Some third-party services that can help automate birthday wishes on Facebook Messenger include:\n\n1. IFTTT (If This Then That): A free service that allows you to create customized recipes based on specific triggers and actions.\n2. Zapier: A platform that automates tasks by connecting different apps and services.\n3. BirthdayBot: A Facebook Messenger bot that helps send birthday messages.\n\nBefore using these services, ensure you understand their:\n\n1. Terms of service\n2. Data privacy policies\n3. Permissions required\n\nYou can also explore Facebook's built-in features, like:\n\n1. Birthday reminders\n2. Scheduled posts\n\nTo set up birthday reminders:\n\n1. Go to Facebook's Events section\n2. Click on Birthdays\n3. Enable notifications for upcoming birthdays\n\nWould you like step-by-step instructions for any of these options?"
